        presente puedes depositarlo en la siguiente cuenta:
      </p>
      <p class='font-semibold'>CVU: 0000007900275009070088</p>
      <p class='font-semibold'>Alias: XV.MIA.QUINCE.UALA</p>
    </span>

    <img
      src='/grupo_mariposas.webp'
      class='absolute top-0 left-0 h-4/5 hidden md:block'
    />
    <img src='/mariposa-marron.webp' class='absolute top-0 left-0 h-32' />
  </section>

  <section
    class='relative pb-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-[#f7f1df]'
  >
    <img src='/icons/festival.gif' class='h-28 md:h-32' />

    <h3 class='w-full text-center text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-12 font-adelia'>
      Música
    </h3>

    <a
      href='https://wa.me/+5493571356409?text=Hola%20M%C3%ADa!%20La%20noche%20de%20tu%20fiesta,%20me%20encantar%C3%ADa%20escuchar%20la%20canci%C3%B3n...%0A'
      class='flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-2 text-lg text-white transition-opacity ease-in-out hover:opacity-85 md:px-10 md:text-xl'
      target='_blank'
    >
      ¿Qué Canción no Debe Faltar?
    </a>

    <img
      src='/grupo_mariposas.webp'
      class='absolute top-0 left-0 h-4/5 hidden md:block'
    />
    <img
      src='/mariposa-marron-cortada.webp'
      class='absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-4/5 hidden md:block'
    />
  </section>

  <section class='flex flex-col relative items-center gap-8 py-16'>
    <img src='/icons/photo.gif' class='h-28 md:h-36' />

    <h3 class='w-full text-center text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-12 font-adelia'>
      Quiero ver tus fotos!
    </h3>

    <span
      class='flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-xl md:text-2xl w-full max-w-[550px] text-center text-pretty'
    >
      <p class='mb-2'>
        Como no quiero perderme ningún detalle de esta noche, te invito a que
        compartas las fotos y me ayudes a inmortalizar estos momentos.
      </p>

      <strong class='text-3xl'>#misxvmia</strong>
    </span>

    <h3
      class='w-full text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-12 font-adelia mt-8 leading-relaxed'
    >
      Te espero para pasar una noche inolvidable!
    </h3>

    <img src='/logo.webp' class='h-40 md:h-56' />

    <img
      src='/imagen-izquierda.webp'
      class='absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-full md:h-4/5 -z-10 scale-x-[-1]'
    />

    <img
      src='/imagen-derecha.webp'
      class='absolute top-0 left-0 h-full md:h-4/5 -z-10 scale-x-[-1]'
    />

    <img src='/mariposa-blanca.webp' class='absolute top-5 left-5 h-32' />
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  #arrow-icon {
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  #left {
    transform: scaleX(-1);
  }

  #hero {
    background-image: url('/background.webp');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: cover;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const countdown = document.getElementById('countdown') as HTMLDivElement
  const goalDate = new Date('2025-03-22T21:00:00').getTime()

  function updateCountdown() {
    const actualDate = new Date().getTime()
    const difference = goalDate - actualDate

    const data = {
      days: Math.floor(difference / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)),
      hours: Math.floor(
        (difference % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60)
      ),
      minutes: Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)),
      seconds: Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60)) / 1000)
    }

    if (difference >= 0) {
      const dateText = `${data.days} Días, ${data.hours}hs, ${data.minutes}m, ${data.seconds}s`
      countdown.innerHTML = dateText
      requestAnimationFrame(updateCountdown)
    } else {
      countdown.innerHTML = '¡Es el día!'
    }
  }

  updateCountdown()
</script>
